title.rendered: VIDEO: Prestige Motorcars X Gas Car Club Morning Run

content.rendered:
Prestige Motorcars has partnered up with GAS Car Club – a community of supercars that’s really starting to make a name for themselves here in Jakarta. Hope you enjoy our official coverage of this morning drive. Lots of nice cars and empty Jakarta highways is always a good choice.
